      Fields in com.genesyslab.platform.configuration.protocol.types declared as CfgAppComponentType 
      Modifier and Type Field Description
      static CfgAppComponentType CfgAppComponentType.CFGAppComponent
      Identifies that application type is a component with its own process that might consist of additional sub-processes (description of which are linked with this application object via Resources) as well as can can host several services (defined as other application objects and linked with this object via Resources)
      static CfgAppComponentType CfgAppComponentType.CFGAppComponentAccessPoint
      Identifies that application type is a virtual access point to the component(s) which are linked with this application object via its Resources
      static CfgAppComponentType CfgAppComponentType.CFGAppComponentService
      Identifies that application type is an service inside a component process (defined by another application object) and not an separate executable
      static CfgAppComponentType CfgAppComponentType.CFGAppComponentSubProcess
      Identifies that application type is an executable process within the component (defined by other application object).
      static CfgAppComponentType CfgAppComponentType.CFGAppComponentUnknown
